==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unswear
<hw>Un*swear"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>swear</ets>.]</ety> <def>To recant or recall, as
an oath; to recall after having sworn; to abjure.</def> <rj><au>J.
Fletcher.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unswear</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Unswear
<hw>Un*swear"</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To recall an oath.</def>
<rj><au>Spenser.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unsweat</ent>⟦br⟧
